description:
This is a sub-function API for tool sex_offenders.
Tool description: National Registered Sex Offenders API for the United States. 750k+ offender records, 1M+ crimes, 19k+ cities, and all 50 states. Supports both criteria-based search (name, city, zip, state) and geospatial search (lat/lng, radius). More info https://offenders.io/
API description: Support 2 types of searches, GIS search (lat, lng, radius) or attribute search (name, city, state, zipcode)

**GIS Search:**
Params:
@lat: latitude
@lng: longitude
@radius: search radius in Miles (Mi), e.g. radius = 0.2 means the API will search for sex offenders within 0.2 miles of the given lat and lng

You can supply additional query params to filter down your results, supported additional params:
@firstName, @lastName, @city, @state, @zipcode

**Attribute Search:**
Params:
@firstName, @lastName, @city,
